        "code": "<!-- REFERENCE SECTION -->\n<section class=\"reference-section\" id=\"reference\">\n  <div class=\"reference-content\">\n    <div class=\"section-badge\">Reference</div>\n    <h2 class=\"section-title\">Co říkají naši klienti</h2>\n    <p class=\"section-description\">Tisíce spokojených klientů z České republiky</p>\n    \n    <!-- Před/Po fotky -->\n    <div class=\"predpo-grid\">\n      <div class=\"predpo-item\">\n        <img src=\"https://mediumseagreen-gaur-406121.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/WhatsApp-Image-2024-05-03-at-16.11.09-1.jpeg\" alt=\"Před a po transplantace\" />\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"predpo-item\">\n        <img src=\"https://mediumseagreen-gaur-406121.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/WhatsApp-Image-2024-05-03-at-16.11.09-2.jpeg\" alt=\"Před a po transplantace\" />\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"predpo-item\">\n        <img src=\"https://mediumseagreen-gaur-406121.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/WhatsApp-Image-2024-05-03-at-16.11.09-3.jpeg\" alt=\"Před a po transplantace\" />\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"predpo-item\">\n        <img src=\"https://mediumseagreen-gaur-406121.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/WhatsApp-Image-2024-08-05-at-11.33.31-1.jpeg\" alt=\"Před a po transplantace\" />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- Recenze Slider -->\n    <div class=\"recenze-slider-wrapper\">\n      <div class=\"recenze-slider\">\n        <div class=\"recenze-track\">\n          <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n            <div class=\"recenze-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Výborná zkušenost od začátku do konce. Profesionální přístup, skvělé výsledky a perfektní komunikace s Michaelou. Cena byla o třetinu nižší než v českých klinikách. Vřele doporučuji!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n              <div class=\"author-avatar\">JP</div>\n              <div class=\"author-info\">\n                <div class=\"author-name\">Jan P.</div>\n                <div class=\"author-meta\">4500 štěpů | DHI metoda</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n            <div class=\"recenze-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Nemohl jsem být spokojenější. Výsledek je přirozený a nikdo nepozná, že jsem podstoupil transplantaci. Michaela byla skvělá - vždy rychle odpovídala a pomohla mi s vším. Děkuji MaxHair!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n              <div class=\"author-avatar\">MK</div>\n              <div class=\"author-info\">\n                <div class=\"author-name\">Martin K.</div>\n                <div class=\"author-meta\">3200 štěpů | Sapphire FUE</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n            <div class=\"recenze-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Kompletní servis na vysoké úrovni. Od transferu z letiště až po pooperační péči - vše perfektně zorganizované. Hotel byl luxusní, doktoři profesionální. Za tu cenu neuvěřitelná hodnota!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n              <div class=\"author-avatar\">TL</div>\n              <div class=\"author-info\">\n                <div class=\"author-name\">Tomáš L.</div>\n                <div class=\"author-meta\">5000 štěpů | DHI metoda</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n            <div class=\"recenze-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Jako žena jsem měla obavy, ale Dr. Merve byla úžasná. Jemný přístup, diskrétní zákrok a krásný přirozený výsledek. Komunikace s Michaelou byla bezproblémová. Doporučuji všem ženám!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n              <div class=\"author-avatar\">KN</div>\n              <div class=\"author-info\">\n                <div class=\"author-name\">Kateřina N.</div>\n                <div class=\"author-meta\">2800 štěpů | Sapphire FUE</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n            <div class=\"recenze-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Transplantace vousů byla nejlepší rozhodnutí. Konečně mám plný vous bez děr. Celý proces byl bezbolestný a rychlý. Cena byla férová a zahrnovala vše. MaxHair - top!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n              <div class=\"author-avatar\">DV</div>\n              <div class=\"author-info\">\n                <div class=\"author-name\">David V.</div>\n                <div class=\"author-meta\">2200 štěpů | DHI metoda</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div class=\"recenze-card\">\n            <div class=\"recenze-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <p class=\"recenze-text\">\"Skvělá investice. Výsledky viditelné už po 6 měsících. Michaela mi pomohla s vším - od konzultace až po pooperační péči. Česká komunikace je velká výhoda. Díky MaxHair!\"</p>\n            <div class=\"recenze-author\">\n              <div class=\"author-avatar\">PH</div>\n              <div class=\"author-info\">\n                <div class=\"author-name\">Petr H.</div>\n                <div class=\"author-meta\">4200 štěpů | DHI metoda</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"slider-controls\">\n        <button class=\"slider-btn slider-btn-prev\" aria-label=\"Předchozí\">\n          <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M15 18L9 12L15 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"slider-dots\"></div>\n        <button class=\"slider-btn slider-btn-next\" aria-label=\"Další\">\n          <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n            <path d=\"M9 18L15 12L9 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <a href=\"/reference\" class=\"btn-secondary\">Všechny reference</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .reference-section {\n    width: 100%;\r\n    max-width: 100vw;\r\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    min-height: 60vh;\n    background: var(--light-gray);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    padding: clamp(50px, 10vw, 100px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px);\n  }\n\n  .reference-content {\n    max-width: 1400px;\n    width: 100%;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .predpo-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n    gap: 24px;\n    margin: 60px 0;\n  }\n\n  .predpo-item {\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .predpo-item:hover {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.3);\n  }\n\n  .predpo-item img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 300px;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    display: block;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-slider-wrapper {\n    margin: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 0;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-slider {\n    overflow: hidden;\n    position: relative;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-track {\n    display: flex;\n    transition: transform 0.5s ease;\n    gap: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);\n  }\n\n  .recenze-card {\n    background: var(--white);\n    border-radius: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 20px);\n    padding: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 32px);\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n    flex: 0 0 calc(33.333% - 22px);\n    min-width: 0;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-card:hover {\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(229, 193, 88, 0.2);\n    transform: translateY(-4px);\n  }\n\n  .recenze-stars {\n    font-size: 24px;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-text {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: var(--dark-brown);\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0 0 24px 0;\n    font-style: italic;\n    opacity: 0.85;\n  }\n\n  .recenze-author {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .author-avatar {\n    width: 56px;\n    height: 56px;\n    background: var(--primary-gold);\n    color: var(--black);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .author-info {\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n\n  .author-name {\n    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--dark-brown);\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .author-meta {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 13px);\n    color: var(--dark-brown);\n    opacity: 0.6;\n  }\n\n  .slider-controls {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: clamp(20px, 3vw, 32px);\n    margin-top: clamp(30px, 4vw, 40px);\n  }\n\n  .slider-btn {\n    width: clamp(44px, 5vw, 48px);\n    height: clamp(44px, 5vw, 48px);\n    background: var(--white);\n    border: 2px solid var(--primary-gold);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    color: var(--primary-gold);\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .slider-btn:hover {\n    background: var(--primary-gold);\n    color: var(--black);\n    transform: scale(1.1);\n  }\n\n  .slider-btn:disabled {\n    opacity: 0.4;\n    cursor: not-allowed;\n  }\n\n  .slider-dots {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: clamp(8px, 1vw, 12px);\n    align-items: center;\n  }\n\n  .slider-dot {\n    width: clamp(10px, 1.2vw, 12px);\n    height: clamp(10px, 1.2vw, 12px);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: var(--medium-gray);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .slider-dot.active {\n    background: var(--primary-gold);\n    width: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 14px);\n    height: clamp(12px, 1.5vw, 14px);\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 1200px) {\n    .predpo-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n    .recenze-card {\n      flex: 0 0 calc(50% - 16px);\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .reference-section {\n      padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 60px) clamp(20px, 4vw, 24px);\n    }\n    .predpo-grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n    .recenze-card {\n      flex: 0 0 100%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  (function() {\n    const slider = document.querySelector('.recenze-track');\n    const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.recenze-card');\n    const prevBtn = document.querySelector('.slider-btn-prev');\n    const nextBtn = document.querySelector('.slider-btn-next');\n    const dotsContainer = document.querySelector('.slider-dots');\n    \n    if (!slider || cards.length === 0) return;\n    \n    let currentIndex = 0;\n    let cardsPerView = window.innerWidth > 1200 ? 3 : window.innerWidth > 768 ? 2 : 1;\n    let totalSlides = Math.ceil(cards.length / cardsPerView);\n    \n    // Vytvoř tečky\n    for (let i = 0; i < totalSlides; i++) {\n      const dot = document.createElement('div');\n      dot.className = 'slider-dot' + (i === 0 ? ' active' : '');\n      dot.addEventListener('click', () => goToSlide(i));\n      dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);\n    }\n    \n    function updateSlider() {\n      const offset = -currentIndex * (100 / cardsPerView);\n      slider.style.transform = `translateX(${offset}%)`;\n      \n      // Aktualizuj tečky\n      const dots = dotsContainer.querySelectorAll('.slider-dot');\n      dots.forEach((dot, i) => {\n        dot.classList.toggle('active', i === currentIndex);\n      });\n      \n      // Aktualizuj tlačítka\n      prevBtn.disabled = currentIndex === 0;\n      nextBtn.disabled = currentIndex === totalSlides - 1;\n    }\n    \n    function goToSlide(index) {\n      currentIndex = Math.max(0, Math.min(index, totalSlides - 1));\n      updateSlider();\n    }\n    \n    function nextSlide() {\n      if (currentIndex < totalSlides - 1) {\n        currentIndex++;\n        updateSlider();\n      }\n    }\n    \n    function prevSlide() {\n      if (currentIndex > 0) {\n        currentIndex--;\n        updateSlider();\n      }\n    }\n    \n    prevBtn.addEventListener('click', prevSlide);\n    nextBtn.addEventListener('click', nextSlide);\n    \n    // Automatické posouvání\n    let autoSlideInterval = setInterval(nextSlide, 5000);\n    \n    // Pozastavit při hover\n    const sliderWrapper = document.querySelector('.recenze-slider-wrapper');\n    if (sliderWrapper) {\n      sliderWrapper.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {\n        clearInterval(autoSlideInterval);\n      });\n      sliderWrapper.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {\n        autoSlideInterval = setInterval(nextSlide, 5000);\n      });\n    }\n    \n    // Responzivní update\n    window.addEventListener('resize', () => {\n      const newCardsPerView = window.innerWidth > 1200 ? 3 : window.innerWidth > 768 ? 2 : 1;\n      if (newCardsPerView !== cardsPerView) {\n        cardsPerView = newCardsPerView;\n        totalSlides = Math.ceil(cards.length / cardsPerView);\n        currentIndex = Math.min(currentIndex, totalSlides - 1);\n        \n        // Recreate dots\n        dotsContainer.innerHTML = '';\n        for (let i = 0; i < totalSlides; i++) {\n          const dot = document.createElement('div');\n          dot.className = 'slider-dot' + (i === currentIndex ? ' active' : '');\n          dot.addEventListener('click', () => goToSlide(i));\n          dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);\n        }\n        \n        updateSlider();\n      }\n    });\n    \n    updateSlider();\n  })();\n</script>",
